{"tid":1356710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"7.27 元朗遊行文宣方向討論","createTime":"2019-07-23T14:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T15:46:43.000Z","uid":287093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"95f1a7b78e3e5c848c11adbd4480ed452e50e3d3","tid":1356710,"uid":287093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得文宣應該要連結最多嘅人，取議題最大公因數（除咗五大訴求）<br />\n會認同「光復香港，時代革命」等嘅人係唔駛文宣都一定會出嚟遊行（包括我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n文宣要爭取嘅係嗰啲因為721好嬲但仍心有餘悸嘅人<br />\n支持大家一齊行落去<br />\n話俾大家聽，想以後都唔駛驚就要一齊行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日劉細良話今次元朗遊行<br />\n應該要話俾策動721元朗恐襲嘅西環聽<br />\n香港人唔怕，唔會因為咁而放棄，唔再堅持行落去<br />\n我覺得講得好啱<br />\n<br />\n我諗咗兩句，拋磚引玉，請大家俾意見：<br />\n<br />\n拒絕恐懼<br />\n堅守良知<br />\n<br />\n只係識用PPT整圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ErEKpb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ErEKpb.jpg&h=3593e056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇唔清究竟幾點喺邊所以無寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n利申：支持勇武嘅和理非"},{"pid":"fbcb4678ed820b8b6497949ede2e5e6b336d1645","tid":1356710,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:36:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得<br />\n１。全面撤回送中<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗暴動</span></span>"},{"pid":"4a7d1df21933ed6cfa510e752df0a1b41e399488","tid":1356710,"uid":287093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:37:53.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58381875637bbfee5d39000c927ee899931fea5","tid":1356710,"uid":287093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488349bc463bdd03dcedbd53da3478a481cd95bb","tid":1356710,"uid":287093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4079c72e3b0057193fb634dab822fb04e6d8a564","tid":1356710,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:40:46.000Z","msg":"強烈要求<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好叫光復！</span></strong></span><br />\n寫信叫鄉紳支持！拉攏鄉議局如侯永強 梁福元系統支持！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>其實大家要識分</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">何君堯係中聯辦系統<br />\n侯強果啲係鄉議局系統<br />\n2邊唔係好妥</span></strong><br />\n叫<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人反黑大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>鄉議局系統 唔係中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n何君堯係西環 <br />\n<br />\n我哋要識挑撥兩個勢力</strong>"},{"pid":"3e6efa63daea159926249a7974c32d3511247d82","tid":1356710,"uid":285270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"支持，柔性一點但堅毅既字眼更加可以爭取最多人入元朗<br />\n721恐襲係觸及人既道德底線，我地係用良知去爭取最多人，包括一家大細，去遊行顯示我地冇俾呢d事震攝到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5882fd132bfe377da6140d34b4b9a007085d7a","tid":1356710,"uid":278138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:56:56.000Z","msg":"唔好叫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復</span>，應該用返<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">保衛西北家園</span>，因為當日被打好多都係西北居民"},{"pid":"3258eb5fa6d54e4db8a6bf1c910bf5a6dab4e4c5","tid":1356710,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">727 強烈建議<span style=\"color: red;\">由「元朗站」行到「兆康站」散</span>，要求行「元朗大馬路」及「青山公路」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n千萬不要變成「民眾鬥民眾」，這是共產黨最喜愛的，如果雙方有傷亡，到時候是非曲直有理說不清，明益警察及政府可以借此收拾殘局！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不要失焦，不要失焦，不要因小失大，報仇誤事，先搞掂狗及王志民<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班鄉黑本來是收錢打人，現在玩大了，全部要交人及著草，冇事唔敢再打人，亦冇人再比錢佢地打人！"},{"pid":"5160404a3e19b29b3efc7da0b0d4efbbcc1a2853","tid":1356710,"uid":278138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3258eb5fa6d54e4db8a6bf1c910bf5a6dab4e4c5","tid":1356710,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">727 強烈建議<span style=\"color: red;\">由「元朗站」行到「兆康站」散</span>，要求行「元朗大馬路」及「青山公路」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n千萬不要變成「民眾鬥民眾」，這是共產黨最喜愛的，如果雙方有傷亡，到時候是非曲直有理說不清，明益警察及政府可以借此收拾殘局！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不要失焦，不要失焦，不要因小失大，報仇誤事，先搞掂狗及王志民<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班鄉黑本來是收錢打人，現在玩大了，全部要交人及著草，冇事唔敢再打人，亦冇人再比錢佢地打人！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:00:36.000Z","msg":"去到兆康太遠同埋經過太多村郊地方，比太多空位人地搞你"},{"pid":"46b9bde267019d7852aa2e905bcdb2025c78d75d","tid":1356710,"uid":287093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"拒絕恐懼<br />\n堅守良知<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ac66f62a21532d6c26355f30f2c58c7c03525e","tid":1356710,"uid":287093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:46:29.000Z","msg":"拒絕恐懼<br />\n堅守良知<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c5c6087ef4f81b7fe56aa4581ed446801d4fd8","tid":1356710,"uid":287093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:46:43.000Z","msg":"拒絕恐懼<br />\n堅守良知<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}